          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", but those odd stories you’re not quite sure how people will take them come along occassionally, which was definitely the case back in August with the video of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "a guy catching the neighbor kid repeatedly playing in his driveway",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/guy-catches-neighbor-kid/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". I ran across this on YouTube since I was already a follower of CanyonChasers, a channel which offers some great, actionable ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
